r.d: Provides bindings to the functions of libssh2 which implements the SSH2 protocol. libssh2 is available from http://libssh2.org/
r.n: - End zend_function_entry ssh2_functions list with PHP_FE_END [PR #67] (Gerdriaan Mulder) - Remove implicit switch-case fallthrough [PR #66] (Gerdriaan Mulder) - Windows build setup with GitHub Actions [PR #75] (Derick Rethans)
